"""Test parsing of ignition delay data points for shock tube file.
        """
file_path = os.path.join('testfile_st.xml')
filename = pkg_resources.resource_filename(__name__, file_path)
tree = etree.parse(filename)
root = tree.getroot()
properties = {}
properties = parse_files_XML.get_datapoints(properties, root)
np.testing.assert_array_equal(properties['temperature'], [1164.48, 1164.97] *
    units.kelvin)
np.testing.assert_array_equal(properties['ignition-delay'], [471.54, 448.03
    ] * units.us)
